item.title: About
item.description: The blog This blog is about everything that the authors want to talk about! The authors Anna Anna is a traveler, yogi, scuba diver and many other things. Between her adventures she enjoys writing Go code, currently developing Wapty. She is now based in San Francisco working with Stripe’s security team. Opinions are her own. Rob Rob is a coder, science lover and glitch magnet. He likes to find weird and unexpected behaviors in anything related to technology.
